name: Cube Dungeon (Woyboy)
description:
A fast-paced 2D Shooter game where you battle through different stages with unique levels and tough enemies. This game is made as a prototype for a much bigger project. As a reflection of it, I learned a lot while making this game, I'll give it my all for the next one.

- Known bug for levels not "counting" all dead enemies. A fix is coming, don't worry.
